{"tid":2510553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大公報男記者涉打12歲女兒 被控虐兒保釋候訊","createTime":"2021-04-30T08:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T08:53:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a31143a5d42f11013d091a48cc2baa2fa49002a","tid":2510553,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"報稱任職大公報記者的男子日前疑在北角家中因女兒衣著問題，動手打女，結果被控一項對看管兒童或少年人襲擊罪，今日在東區裁判法院提堂。案件押後至6月11日再訊，涉案男記者獲准以5,000元保釋外出，其間不得騷擾控方證人、即其女兒。<br />\n<br />\n45歲張姓被告，其英文版的控罪書指明他為大公報記者（ Reporter of Ta Kung Pao），中文版控罪書則寫為「其他職業」。控罪指被告於今年4月27日在北角馬寶道62號至76號華禮大廈一個單位內，對一名12歲的兒童或少年人、即女孩X負有管養、看管或照顧責任的人，故意襲擊該女孩X，其方式相當可能導致該女孩X受到不必要的苦楚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/PCEBHLMSHRDVNHFYE5GUEEZ33A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FPCEBHLMSHRDVNHFYE5GUEEZ33A%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=e3fdbb6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FPCEBHLMSHRDVNHFYE5GUEEZ33A%2F&h=53c874df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/PCEBHLMSHRDVNHFYE5GUEEZ33A/</a>"},{"pid":"e94497d946ed916b09faa30a98acbd47f2ccf344","tid":2510553,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:44:44.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />暴力就唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7461ee6568cdb0eff6933cc6395900b55c3c409f","tid":2510553,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">其間不得騷擾控方證人、即其女兒</span><br />\n諗起低俗喜劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2caf8f4e66a5f3dcb436fc56ecee1da60c4ac090","tid":2510553,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f28c165dfadf65a127c5fb330a93ff973bd5ae5","tid":2510553,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:45:51.000Z","msg":"連登仔：一定係個女著到成隻雞咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc24a4828cb014d6e75b3d3100beaf58c720bba3","tid":2510553,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"大公報記者<br />\n啫係支那賤畜記者<br />\n佢殺咗個女我都唔意外"},{"pid":"9328ca3d54f11d8a799f357dad3b67e4b874d39b","tid":2510553,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"黑記打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5284b085ac7320da2474f8689938334be486164","tid":2510553,"uid":295735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"大公報記者好失禮你呀！中文做乜報其他職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043ce6210222abd5d55327058e2c041522a4a456","tid":2510553,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"高尚情操，對社會有貢獻，不提證供起訴啦<br />\n查兩查隨時懷疑有人用塊面襲擊老豆隻手添啦"},{"pid":"28f476d64a4d78adecf9226e5f23838bb97e6e6f","tid":2510553,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:51:37.000Z","msg":"紅媒同黑警一樣都係鐘意打小朋友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdgVKNeuw5dNjFWcZJfWwvzbQdRPmj15TXETg4HNJPTon?filename=S0mObSR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS0mObSR.gif&h=1afceb73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a603fa670c8838a3c071e3cdad36b5db0f338c5","tid":2510553,"uid":260901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"記者無特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}